title: War of the Roses: She asked for cash AFTER he already got her a present
description: Brian has been seeing Jayna since the summer and got her a really nice Valentine's Day present but it wasn't good enough for her so he gave her more.  She didn't even get him anything.  Is Jayna using him or is there a miscommunication about their relationship, OR is there something else going on?
